1. Ja sam *popio* kafu pre nego što sam krenuo na posao. (I drank coffee before going to work.)
2. Ti *popiješ* sok za doručak, zar ne? (You drink juice for breakfast, don't you?)
3. Oni su *popili* sve pivo sinoć. (They drank all the beer last night.)
4. Mi smo *popili* čašu vode nakon treninga. (We drank a glass of water after the workout.)
5. Vi ćete *popiti* piće s nama kasnije? (Will you drink with us later?)
6. Ona ne voli da *popije* alkohol. (She doesn't like to drink alcohol.)
7. Kada se budiš, prvo *popij* čašu vode. (When you wake up, drink a glass of water first.)
8. Sutra ujutru moram *popiti* lekove pre doručka. (Tomorrow morning, I have to take medicine before breakfast.)
9. Da li želiš *popiti* kafu sa mnom kasnije? (Do you want to have coffee with me later?)
10. Deca su *popila* sve mleko iz frižidera. (The children drank all the milk from the fridge.)